node.text: Last night to sign up for the Ike Foundation Pro Am this Sat. June 5th on the Upper Chesapeake Bay! First place wins a Basscat/Yamaha valued at over 30K and all the proceeds go towards kids fishing! Sign up at theikefoundation.org or SWIPE UP in my story! @theikefoundation

node.title: Last night to sign upFor the Ike Foundation Pro Am! First place wins a Bass

node.text: I’ve put A LOT of time and work into becoming a decent kayak angler. I’ve had to relearn and practice new ways to catch and target fish. All the hard work paid off last weekend with my FIRST official pro kayak WIN! Feels even better that it happened in my NEW Ike Approved Hobie! @hobiefishing @teamtoyota @lowrancefishing @torqeedo_fishing @power.pole 📸 Photo Cred: BASS @daltontumblin.photography

node.text: What an incredible day fishing the BASS Pro Kayak event on the Upper Chesapeake Bay! I’ve been close before, but it was amazing to finally win one of these things! DEF a check off my bucket list! A last minute 18.50 largemouth, helped me cull up for the win! Also, I was in my NEW Ike Approved Hobie kayak and that made it even more special! @hobiefishing @aftcofreshwater @lowrancefishing @power.pole

node.text: Folks at Home! The VMC Ned Rig Jig is the ultimate smallmouth killer! This bait is designed with a custom hybrid hook to increase hook up ratios and comes in 4 sizes! This is my go to pick combined with a berkley lil general or water bug when targeting smallmouth! Swipe up link in my story !!@berkleyfishing @abugarcia_fishing @vmchooks @tacklewarehouse
